<br>
Nobody outside of a few folks like Rynnia(probably, he seems to manage to know every ebay transaction that happens on this server) really knew who was doing it - they were using twinks for delivery, etc, but my understanding is that (like Rynnia) they were making quite a good 'living'.<br>
<br>
At some point post-kunark and post-epics, for reasons I can't even possibly guess at, Shortman decided he was done with EQ, or at least with E/V and his Ebay business.  The character went up for sale (without a name, of course), and I think many people were caught by surprise, as he'd been one of the more high-profile &quot;original&quot; E/V crew, ala Steele, Crush, etc.<br>
<br>
That's the &quot;gossip&quot; version, only what I picked up over the years from hearing stuff and reading the old trib boards on everlore and Talamay's board.  I'd expect an old-time E/V member at this point to reply with a &quot;yeah, that's close enough to what happened&quot; or a &quot;no, not really.&quot;  But I think that's the high-level history! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/bthetribunaldotorg.showUserPublicProfile?gid=dextromethorphanhydrobromide>DextroMethorphan hydrobromide</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Lurker</span><br>  Posts: 38<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/11/03 8:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthetribunaldotorgfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2522.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re:</span><hr size=1> anyone have a link to the original trib board?  the one before Talamay's.  Where Crush flamed Rynnia when he made 60 first?  Been wanting to read it again for awhile, just lost the link. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#4D4D4D><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/bthetribunaldotorg.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ladidahohum>Ladida Hohum</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Will no one rid me of<BR>
