Ok, I started it, and I've got basically what I expected.  Now to tell you where he went after the first &quot;Shortman&quot; persona left.  I dont' know the original buyer, but I DO know it was someone already playin on this server, and frequently.  From that person, I assume he transferred account owners at least 2 more times before MY history with him starts.  I know of the identity of ONE owner before I attained him, and I know at least 1 other person that &quot;Drove&quot; him for awhile, but I'll leave them anon, for the sake of thier own Reputations. I know they never &quot;Purchased&quot; Shortman, they were handed him just as I was handed him.  <br>
<br>
That's right, I owned Shortman last.  He was handed to me from a guildmate in the guild of WWC, or White Wolf Clan for any of you who haven't been around long enough to remember them.  We haven't been a guild for a LONG LONG time, but alot of old timers remember us.  We were a good guild to start people off, but we never reached the post Naggy/Vox raids except for later on with KoT. But that's all a different story, back to Shortman.....I attained him one day when the last owner decided &quot;they&quot; didn't want to play the game anymore.  They were leaving EQ, and gave away most everything they owned.  Shortman went to the guild, as a gift, and since I was a friend of this benevolent person, and I was one of very few people online in the guild at the time, the info was passed to me, and I started his account anew, taking over payments.  <br>
<br>
I played Shortman for prolly about 9 months total, he wasn't my Main, simply a &quot;Guild Cleric&quot; that I used on occasional raids for rezz's or &quot;Uber&quot; heals and such.  I got to like playin him, and TRIED to re establish his name as one of honesty and good will.  I started something I personally liked calling &quot;Drive By Rezzing&quot; where whenever I saw a dead body, i would automatically do a /who all and ask if they wanted an epic rezz, I'd then rezz them, heal em and run off.  <br>
<br>
I recieved TONS of tells calling me all sorts of names, and eventually I tired of EQ altogether, and I retired.  Someone decided they weren't happy with me quiting, or saw opportunity knocking, and proceded to hack my computer, I lost not only the Shortman account, but 2 other accounts in the doing.  I got the passwords reset on 2 of those, but Shortman was lost forever, and my other 2 accounts were stripped down to nothing, my Original Main, Lazarux, still remains nearly Nekkid.  I've retired him permanently, and started Reptylle.  He is my current main, and will remain my &quot;Main&quot; until I tire of him, or quit the game.<br>
<br>
I started this thread to give a finallity to the character of Shortman, for those that hated him, be happy, for those that got rezzed by him, I'm glad I could help at times.  I also wanted it to be known that at least 2 owners of Shortman, Myself and the owner before me, Never paid a cent for the char or any of his gear. When i recieved him, he had only his Planar gear (Hate) and like Donals Guants, Boots and Arms....the rest was gone.  I also wanted you all to know who he was in the end, and just kinda put an end to the speculation of what finally happened to him, I'm not sure if the original owner reset the passwords and resold him, or deleted him, or he's just sitting in someones computer collecting dust, I just know the last time I had him, and what I tried to do.<br>
<br>
I'm not wanting flamed for any of this, or lookin for sympathy or awe or any other bullshit, just kinda putting a bit more into the books as official history, if that is what you all want to call it.<br>
<br>
Thanks for yer time, and I'm still playin, if ya have any questions, or can fill me in on the lost time between the initial Sale and the time when he was given to me, just call me Curious.<br>
<br>
Respectfully, <br>
<br>
Reptylle Bloodscayle<br>
